                    span.coach-stats__small OF EXPIRIENCE
                .coach-stats__item 
                    span.coach-stats__big 156K
                    span.coach-stats__small FOLLOWING ME
        .advantages 
            .wrapper 
                h1.advantages__title
                    |   The journey to a healthier 
                    |   body starts right now
                a(href="#").advantages__button.button 
                    |   ONLINE COACHING
                .advantages__content 
                    .advantage-card 
                        img(src="./img/advantage-1.webp" width="300" height="300" alt="Image of jumping woman").advantage-card__image
                        h2.advantage-card__title 
                            |   Learn to live a healthy 
                            |   life with fitness
                        span.advantage-card__description 
                            |   Changing your lifestyle with a fast paced life may seem 
                            |   hard or impossible, but with small steps each week you 
                            |   can achieve your dream physique and live a healthier 
                            |   life.
                    .advantage-card 
                        img(src="./img/advantage-2.webp" width="300" height="300" alt="Image of man and big wheel").advantage-card__image
                        h2.advantage-card__title 
                            |   Understand how to do 
                            |   excercises properly
                        span.advantage-card__description 
                            |   Just going to the gym and lifting weights won't make 
                            |   you healthy, after all it may even cause some harm to 
                            |   your body. We teach proper exercise techniques
                    .advantage-card 
                        img(src="./img/advantage-3.webp" width="300" height="300" alt="Image of man and bottle").advantage-card__image
                        h2.advantage-card__title 
                            |   Track your 
                            |   progress weekly
                        span.advantage-card__description 
                            |   We're tracking your goal weight with body fat measures, 
                            |   weight and general feeling. You may have the same 
                            |   body weight but feel 10x better.
                    .advantage-card 
                        img(src="./img/benefit.webp" width="300" height="300" alt="Image of woman and timer").advantage-card__image
                        h2.advantage-card__title 
                            |   Follow a specific plan 
                            |   made just for you
                        span.advantage-card__description 
                            |   Everyone is different, and we know it. That's why all of 
                            |   our clients get a programme specific just for their 
                            |   lifestyle and body tipe. This give the best possible 
                            |   results.
